# Backend Architecture Rules

- Use microservices with clear separation: Incident, Case, Arrest, Warrant, Evidence, Dispatch, Map, Notification, Document, Admin.
- All services must expose REST endpoints with proper HTTP status codes.
- JWT expiry: 15 minutes; refresh token: 7 days.
- RBAC middleware required on every protected route.
- Audit logs must record user ID, timestamp, IP, and before/after state.
